          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Provide a callback function for the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "onTextChange",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " attribute to respond to changes in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "searchField",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "textField",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " elements. You can respond to user inputs as the changes happen. This attribute must be set to a function; for example, ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Keyboard.onTextChange = function () {}",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
